HEADWORD: Managery
<hw>Man"age*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>menagerie</ets>, <ets>mesnagerie</ets>. See <er>Manage</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, and cf. <er>Menagerie</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
